<body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <h1>Space Dock</h1>
        <h2>About</h1>
        <p class="lead">
        Space Dock is an application for Macintosh, iOS and Android for putting together squadrons 
        for <a href="http://wizkidsgames.com">WizK!d's</a> excellent <a href="http://wizkidsgames.com/startrek/star-trek-attack-wing">Star Trek: Attack Wing</a> game.
        </p>
        <p>Modest efforts are made to make sure Space Dock is working correctly when released but glitches happen. Make sure to export your most valuable squad designs for safe keeping.</p>
        <p>Space Dock Mac requires a Mac running OS X 10.8 or later due to a dependency on application development features available in that version or later.</p>
        <p>Space Dock iOS requires iOS version 6 or later.</p>
        <p>Space Dock Android requires Android version 4.0 or later.</p>
        <p>Questions about Space Dock? Comment? Email me at <a href="mailto:rob@tsuk.com">rob@tsuk.com</a>.</p>
        <h2>Download</h1>
          <p>
            <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/st-space-dock/id740765008?mt=8&uo=4" target="itunes_store" style="display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(https://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/htmlResources/assets/en_us//images/web/linkmaker/badge_appstore-lrg.png) no-repeat;width:135px;height:40px;@media only screen{background-image:url(https://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/htmlResources/assets/en_us//images/web/linkmaker/badge_appstore-lrg.svg);}"></a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.funnyhatsoftware.spacedock">
              <img alt="Get it on Google Play"
                   src="en_generic_rgb_wo_45.png" />
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <a class="btn btn-large btn-primary" href="space_dock_b<%= max_build_number %>.zip">Download for Mac</a>
          </p>
          <h2>Testing</h1>
          <p>If you'd like to help test versions of Space Dock for iOS before they are released to the store please visit <a href="https://www.testflightapp.com/install/bc30b610b55233bf7eab914f389c1461-MTE4NzY1MzU/">this page at TestFlight</a>. Since test devices are limited to 100 please only sign up if you will actually install and use test versions.</p>
            <p>If you'd like to help test versions of Space Dock for Android before they are released to the store please join <a href="https://plus.sandbox.google.com/communities/101516757258980614422">testing Google+ community</a> and ask to join. Once joined
              you can download the alpha test version from <a href="https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.funnyhatsoftware.spacedock">the Google Play store</a>.</p>
              <p>If you'd like to help test versions of Space Dock for Mac before they are released please email me at <a href="mailto:rob@tsuk.com">rob@tsuk.com</a>. If there's enough interest I'll set up a Mac test group.</p>
        <h2>Development</h1>
          Space Dock is open source software. If you're interested in perusing the source code or helping out with development you can visit the <a href="https://github.com/rtsuk/spacedock">repository on GitHub</a>.
